much\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/01\/gives-everything-away\/","url_meta":{"origin":10148,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Charity: The Prophet gives everything away before he dies","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was in the severe agony of his final illness and he had seven or nine gold coins. The Prophet said, \u201cO Aisha, what have you done with this gold?\u201d I said, \u201cIt is with me.\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7683,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/prophet-wife-mood-aisha\/","url_meta":{"origin":10148,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: The Prophet can recognize his wife&#8217;s mood","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIndeed, I can tell when you are angry or pleased with me.\u201d I said, \u201cHow do you know that, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, when you are pleased, you say: Yes, by the Lord\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuam